title: The dark stars(idea for a new champ??)
body: We are the dark stars, we seek to consume the world. our master still sleeps, but not for long.

replies.body:
We are the harbingers of doom. We are those whom seek for the destruction of your world, we seek to consume, yet we wait, biding our time for our mastery sleeps... But not for long.
